index 00000000..762dceb6
--- /dev/null
+++ b/docs/update.md
@@ -0,0 +1,17 @@
+# Update Hive
+
+`hive update` delegates to the install channel that owns the binary.
+
+- Homebrew: `brew upgrade <org>/hive/hive`
+- AUR: configured helper, for example `yay -Syu hive-bin`
+- Script installer: re-runs the release `install.sh` URL recorded in
+  `~/.config/hive/install_receipt.yml`
+
+If Hive cannot identify the install channel, it prints a manual update
+recommendation and does not mutate binaries.
+
+Preview the delegated command:
+
+```bash
+hive update --dry-run
+```
