+# Script Installer
+
+The fallback installer is:
+
+```bash
+curl -fsSL https://github.com/<org>/hive/releases/download/v0.1.0/install.sh | bash
+```
+
+The script:
+
+- detects macOS arm64, Ubuntu-style Linux x86_64 glibc, and Arch x86_64;
+- prefers Homebrew on macOS and AUR helpers on Arch when present;
+- falls back to downloading the matching GitHub Release tarball;
+- verifies SHA256 before installing;
+- installs to `~/.local/bin` by default;
+- creates XDG config/data/state/cache directories;
+- writes `~/.config/hive/install_receipt.yml` for `hive update`;
+- chooses `hv` when an unrelated `hive` executable is already first on `PATH`;
+- prints dependency hints instead of installing tools silently.
+
+Set `HIVE_INSTALL_PREFER_NATIVE=0` to force direct release-artifact install.
+Set `HIVE_INSTALL_DRY_RUN=1` to inspect actions without mutating the system.
